#, no-c-format
msgid "Translations"
msgstr "Vertalingen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4699
#, no-c-format
msgid "Translations were contributed by the &kde; translators."
msgstr "Vertalingen zijn geleverd door de vertalers van &kde;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:4703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special Thanks"
msgstr "Speciale dank aan"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:4705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &smb4k; team would like to thank everyone who contributed by sending "
"patches. Also, a big \"Thank you!\" goes to Rashid N. Achilov "
"<email>shelton@sentry.granch.ru</email>, who convinced us to port &smb4k; to "
"FreeBSD and helped us a great deal to achieve this goal."
msgstr ""
"Het &smb4k;-team wil iedereen bedanken die heeft bijgedragen door patches in "
"te sturen. Er gaat ook een grote \"Thank you!\" naar Rashid N. Achilov "
"<email>shelton@sentry.granch.ru</email>, die ons wist te overtuigen om "
"&smb4k; te porten naar FreeBSD en ons veel heeft geholpen om dit doel te "
"bereiken."

#~ msgid "2024-12-30"
#~ msgstr "2024-12-30"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Unmount the selected shares. If no share is selected in the shares view, "
#~ "this button is disabled."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Koppelt de geselecteerde gedeelde mappen af. Als u in het venster geen "
#~ "gedeelde mappen hebt geselecteerd dan is deze knop niet te selecteren."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Unmount all shares at once. If you do not have any shares mounted, this "
#~ "button is disabled."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Koppelt alle shares tegelijk af. Als u geen shares heeft aangekoppeld dan "
#~ "is deze knop niet te selecteren."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "One or multiple selected shares may be unmounted by either clicking the "
#~ "<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>U</"
#~ "keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenuitem>Unmount</guimenuitem></"
#~ "menuchoice> action, or by pressing its keyboard shortcut. By default, the "
#~ "ability to unmount a share is restricted to the ones that are owned by "
#~ "you. This behavior can be altered in the <link linkend="
#~ "\"configuration_page_mounting_basic_settings_behavior\">configuration "
#~ "dialog</link>. If you enabled the unmounting of shares that are owned by "
